p:
Template search for homology modeling of protein with Blast
22 and HHBlits
23 has been made against the SWISS-MODEL template library (SMTL, last updated on 2020-04-08 and last included in PDB release on 2020-04-03). A total of 63 templates for the target sequence are found with Blast
22 . Similarly, a total of 110 templates are found for HHBlits
23 .
